Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father was hopping mad, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't do anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After what those guys said about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato, do you understand\Nwhy Father's forbidden you to fight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have tremendous power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But excessive power can end up\Nhurting not just others...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you yourself as well, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At any rate, you're\Nstill too young, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then when can I start?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess when you find what it is\Nthat you're supposed to do, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I'm supposed to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. And that will probably be the day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that you decide how you're\Ngoing to use that power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you already found "what it is that\Nyou're supposed to do," Big Sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I'm supposed to do\Nis protect you, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And for me, that's the most\Nimportant thing of all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then... Then I'm going to\Nprotect you, too, Big Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That will be my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.46,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ser Veresta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, is that you, Julis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a coincidence!\NFancy meeting you here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You! What are you doing here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell are you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! He's that transfer student!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Ayato Amagiri. Nice to meet you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awesome! Awesome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, who said you could record this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lester, pushing it any further\Nwould be a bad idea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm not giving up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna make you acknowledge\Nmy abilities if it's the last thing I do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First the duel this morning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now your cool-headedness\Nin confronting Lester...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really are a tough one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be quite the spectacle, seeing\Nhow long that look of innocence will last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't as forgiving a place\Nas you think, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then why are you fighting here, Julis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a princess, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in need of money, you see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I'm fighting here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First off, the Phoenix Festa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the first thing I've got to conquer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then have you already found a partner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Phoenix is a tag-team Festa, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Julis, don't you have any friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's not because I don't have any friends\Nthat I haven't found a partner yet, all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, it is true that I have no friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's irrelevant!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I simply haven't found anyone\Nwho meets my standards as a partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you readily admit that\Nyou don't have any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, what kind of\Npartner are you looking for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, beggars can't be choosers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but at most, someone with\NPage One-level combat skills,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who has a quick mind, a strong will,\Nand a noble spirit, much like a knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}High bar, much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoops, my deadline's coming up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, guys, I'm out of here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose I'll be heading back myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey... uh... Julis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-Which way's the boys' dorm again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After what you went through\Nthis morning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You could at least do your homework\Nand study the guide map!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I just thought, "so you do\Nlaugh like that sometimes."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-Where did that come from?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I've been known to laugh at times!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you go straight that way, you'll come\Nto a path that leads to the boys' dorm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just keep to it from there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now what?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would you mind showing me around\Nthe academy sometime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And while we're at it, the city, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that some kind of joke?!\NWhy should I?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you said yourself that you'd\Ndo anything I asked, just once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, I did say that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But is that all you want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. First, I've got to\Nget used to this academy, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose it can't be helped.\NA debt is a debt, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, then, I'll show you around\Nthe academy tomorrow after class,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we'll tour the city on\Nour next day off... How's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did that princess actually\Nreturn someone's greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-How rude is that, you wretches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even I am known\Nto return greetings, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Saya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?\NYou guys know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... What a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you\Nsince you moved overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so does that make it six years or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm totally in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you haven't changed\Nat all, have you, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're exactly\Nthe way you were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten taller, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta say, what a small world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This might even be one of\Nthose fateful reunions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fateful reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well-put, Yabuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's your dad doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost doing too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I came here is\Nbecause Dad told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to get some exposure\Nfor the gun he invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had my own reasons, too.\NSo I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And what would that reason be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better not get any tasteless ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha, loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right,\Nsit yourselves down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Homeroom's now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't you, Sasamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why were you\Na no-show yesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear you out, so talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I merely overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you overslept, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh... ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! How many times\Nhave you pulled this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking a make-up class\Non your next day off, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you still have trouble\Ngetting up in the morning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bed holds me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that park\Nwe always used to play in as kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Where there was\Na huge lake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! Remember when we...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A promise is a promise, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis's going to give me\Na tour of the academy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riessfeld is? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because... Well, it's quite complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no concern of yours, Sasamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show Ayato around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said "I have no choice," Riessfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you shouldn't have\Na problem with me taking your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately, I have no intention of\Nbreaking a promise I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I think Ayato would rather\Nhave me than a guide who's not into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm not into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, whereas you just\Nstarted here this year, Sasamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who's been here since\Njunior high, I'd make a far better guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well! If that's the criteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then that certainly makes me\Nthe most qualified, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Julis transferred in\Nduring our third year of junior high,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I've been a bona fide\Nstudent here since first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, before you do anything else,\Nget away from me, Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness, you're all so callous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm here, I wanted to\Njoin in on the fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Permission denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't I just\Ntake care of business and withdraw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look... They're touching me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I mentioned the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your Lux weapon selection and\Ncompatibility test will be held tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no issues,\Nplease sign those documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you're here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the student council president is\Nhand-delivering mere documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you must have a lot of\Ntime on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as our students are all such good children,\Nit makes our jobs so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering about this\Nyesterday, but are you two friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, indeed we are!\N- Not on your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, how cold we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're longtime acquaintances
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who've run into each other at\Nthe Vienna Opera House Ball several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done here, then\Nwhy don't you take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo, shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, tomorrow I'm going to\Nhave Ayato all to myself, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,consider yourself warned!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that vixen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting so carried away just because\Nher breasts are somewhat large!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day, those things\Nare nothing but fat, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! All right, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,since you're both here, maybe I'll\Nhave you both show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Both of us?\N- Both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why not? It would be a pain\Nto argue any further, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Club Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose you'll be\Nmaking your way here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when you want to lodge\Na complaint with the media clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Committee Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any issues with your\Nbenefits, you need to go through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are seven different\Nplaces to eat on campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but since this underground cafeteria is\Noften relatively empty, you should use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Sasamiya, it's not like\NI'm showing you around, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but I'm directionally-challenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm amazed that you still\Ninsisted on giving the tour yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get us some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riessfeld, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to show Ayato around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I owed him, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owed him how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of a duel, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you dueled Ayato, Riessfeld?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were interrupted midway.\NSo the duel was voided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about it doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After dueling Ayato, there's no way\Nthat you'd live to tell the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're powerful, Riessfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at best, you're about my level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not good enough\Nto take on Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of swagger, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Want to test that theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those arrows...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The same as that other one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I've been caught off-guard yet again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Longiflorum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A 38-type Lux grenade\Nlauncher, the Helnekrom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A grenade launcher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lot more\Nextreme than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not as much as you, Riessfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at me, you're so dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking! I'm not looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, totally see-through.\NNow this is lurid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! At least try to cover\Nyourself a bit, too, Sasamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You... where are\Nyour undergarments?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tragic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you had quite a time yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.52,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEIDOUKAN ACADEMY TOP 5 ATTACKED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the suspects\Nwill be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, that might prove difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Disciplinary Committee\Nhas been investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the suspect is nowhere to be found,\Nand not a clue in sight, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, wasn't\Nyesterday's incident a clear-cut crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- If that's the case...\N- Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Asterisk does have its own police force,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:13.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STAR HUNTER POLICE UNIT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but its jurisdiction doesn't\Nextend to the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only Julis were\Na bit more cooperative,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there'd be measures that we could take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's like, "No need for\Nan investigation or bodyguards."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she being so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, it's all that girl can do\Nto protect what's in her own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should she try to\Nacquire something new,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what she already has could\Nslip through her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's in her own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is our other Ogre Lux applicant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you two already\Nmet, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the process\Nfor renting out a Lux?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We measure your compatibility\Nwith the Lux you're requesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if it's over 80%, you can check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Mr. MacPhail's\Nchosen the Ser Veresta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's the Ser Veresta...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ogre Lux that my\Nsister might have used.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're ready to start testing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please begin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Current compatibility rate... 32%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about the Ogre Luxes having\Nsomething like a will of their own, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is that what I'm seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that his power-at-all-costs\Nmindset is all that repulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, the Ser Veresta can't\Nbe persuaded by force alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I, too, am an Ogre Lux wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Why won't you obey me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do as I say, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The compatibility rate's\Nslipped into negative territory!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Proceeding any further\Nwould be dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please withdraw immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't like being pestered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect of you,\NAyato. That was masterful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C-Compatibility... 97%!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Condition... all green!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do you think they'll be okay\Nwith passing this on to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato?{\i0}
